# Project Context: ADVA - Atelier des Verre & Acier

## Project Overview
This project is the professional vitrine site for **ADVA (Atelier des Verre & Acier)**, an architecture agency led by Nicolas Claudet (Architecte DPLG). The site emphasizes technical expertise, structural rigor, and administrative clarity through a modern, minimal, and architectural aesthetic.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework:** React 19.2.0 with Vite 7.2.4
- **3D Engine:** Three.js 0.182.0 with `@react-three/fiber` 9.4.2 and `@react-three/drei` 10.7.7
- **State Management:** Zustand 5.0.10
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS 4.1.18 (via `@tailwindcss/postcss`)
- **Build Tool:** Vite with React plugin
- **Linting:** ESLint 9.39.1 with React hooks and refresh plugins
- **Fonts:** Montserrat (Display/Titles) and Roboto (Sans/Body) from Google Fonts
- **Deployment:** GitHub Pages (base path: `/adva_website/`) with CI/CD workflow

## Architecture & Conventions
- **Modular Structure:**
    - `src/components/ui/`: Standard React components for HTML/CSS interface (Navbar, Hero, Projects, ProjectModal, About, Footer)
    - `src/components/canvas/`: Three.js/Fiber components for 3D scenes (Scene.jsx)
    - `src/hooks/`: Custom hooks for complex logic (directory exists, ready for use)
    - `src/store/`: Zustand stores for global state management (useStore.js - manages modal state: selectedProject, setSelectedProject, closeModal)
    - `src/data/`: Static data files (projects.js with project data structure)
- **Components:** Functional components with React hooks (no class components)
- **3D Assets:** 3D models (`.glb`) should be placed in `src/assets/` or `public/` (configured in vite.config.js)
- **Styling:** Use Tailwind CSS utility classes. Custom styles in `src/index.css` with theme configuration
- **File Naming:** PascalCase for components (e.g., `Hero.jsx`, `ProjectModal.jsx`), camelCase for utilities, hooks, and stores (e.g., `useStore.js`, `projects.js`)

## Current Implementation

### Components Structure
- **Navbar.jsx**: Fixed navigation with:
  - Smooth scroll links (Projets, L'Agence, Contact) that automatically close modal if open
  - Logo "ADVA" clickable - scrolls to portfolio section if not already visible
  - Uses Zustand store to close modal before navigation
  - Uppercase typography with tracking
- **Hero.jsx**: Full-screen hero section with:
  - Animated title "Atelier des Verre & Acier" with enhanced drop-shadow
  - **Carousel background**: Rotating images from the first 4 projects (auto-advance every 5 seconds)
  - Subtle white overlay (bg-white/40) for text readability
  - Smooth image transitions with zoom effect (scale-110) and opacity fade
  - Clickable carousel indicators at bottom (horizontal lines, opacity-based)
  - Scroll indicator ("Découvrir") below carousel indicators
  - Uses `id="hero"` for navigation targeting
  - Imports projects data for carousel functionality
- **Projects.jsx**: Portfolio section with:
  - Dynamic category filtering (Tous, Logements Collectifs, Logements Individuels, Médico-Social, Hôtellerie / Tertiaire)
  - Grid layout with hover effects
  - Project modal trigger on click
  - Project cards with images, titles, descriptions, categories, cities, and status badges
  - Uses Zustand store for modal state management (selectedProject from store)
- **ProjectModal.jsx**: Full-screen modal displaying:
  - High z-index (z-[9999]) to prevent content overlap
  - Technical data overlay on hero image (Maître d'ouvrage, Mission, Surface, Budget)
  - Identity sidebar ("Identité Constructive" with ADVA branding)
  - Hero image, title, description
  - Photo gallery and technical plans
  - Smooth animations and transitions
  - Prevents body scroll when open (overflow: hidden)
  - Automatically closes when navigating via Navbar links
- **About.jsx**: "L'Agence" section with:
  - Team members (Nicolas Claudet, Hélène Digol, David Monti) with roles and emails
  - Mission descriptions, project typologies, and commitments
  - Two-column responsive layout
- **Footer.jsx**: Contact section with:
  - Address: 15 Parc de la Risle, 76130 Mont-Saint-Aignan
  - Phone: 02 35 61 27 10
  - Email: n.claudet@adva-architectes.fr
  - LinkedIn link
  - Embedded Google Maps
- **Scene.jsx**: 3D background with:
  - Infinite architectural grid (subtle, low opacity)
  - Float animation
  - White background (#FFFFFF)
  - Studio environment preset

