### Design System
- **Color Palette:**
  - Background: #FFFFFF (pure white)
  - Text: #333333 (anthracite)
  - Accents: Opacity variations (10%, 20%, 30%, 40%, 50%, 60%, 80%)
- **Typography:**
  - Display/Titles: Montserrat (font-display) - bold, uppercase, tight tracking
  - Body/Sans: Roboto (font-sans) - regular weight, relaxed leading
  - Font sizes: Responsive with viewport units for hero, fixed sizes for body
- **Spacing:** Generous whitespace, large padding (px-8 md:px-24), section gaps (gap-24, gap-32)
- **Animations:** Subtle fade-ins, slide-ins, zoom effects with duration-700/1000, smooth transitions
- **Effects:** 
  - Grayscale images that become colored on hover
  - Opacity transitions, scale transforms
  - Carousel image zoom effect (scale-110) with smooth transitions
  - Background carousel with fade transitions (duration-1000ms)
  - White overlay for text readability over images

### State Management
- Zustand store (`useStore.js`) manages global modal state:
  - `selectedProject`: Currently selected project object (null when closed)
  - `setSelectedProject(project)`: Opens modal with project data
  - `closeModal()`: Closes modal by setting selectedProject to null
  - Used by Navbar (to close modal on navigation) and Projects (to manage modal state)

### Deployment
- **GitHub Pages:** Configured with base path `/adva_website/`
- **CI/CD:** GitHub Actions workflow (`.github/workflows/deploy.yml`) automatically builds and deploys on push to main
- **Manual deploy:** `npm run deploy` script available
- **URL:** `https://moombba.github.io/adva_website/`

